---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout 
  title="Privacy Policy | Restoration AI"
  description="Privacy Policy for Restoration AI. Learn how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information."
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-24 max-w-4xl">
    <div class="bg-[#020617] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl relative overflow-hidden">
      <!-- Glow effect -->
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-full blur-[80px] -z-10"></div>
      
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 tracking-tight">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8 font-medium">Last Updated: June 4, 2026</p>
      
      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-blue max-w-none text-slate-300">
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Restoration AI ("Company", "we", "our", "us") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting the personal information that you share with us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our websites (restorationai.io and app.restorationai.io), our AI communication tools, and our related services (collectively, the "Services").
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-200 mt-6 mb-3">A. Information You Provide to Us</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, company details, and payment information when you register for our Services.</li>
          <li><strong>Communications:</strong> Recordings, transcriptions, and metadata of phone calls routed through our AI Receptionist agents.</li>
          <li><strong>Customer Data:</strong> Contact lists, client information, and job details you upload or input into our platform to utilize our dispatch and marketing features.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-200 mt-6 mb-3">B. Information Automatically Collected</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> IP addresses, browser types, device information, and diagnostic data related to your use of our platform.</li>
          <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> We use cookies and tracking technologies to maintain user sessions, remember preferences, and analyze site traffic.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-200 mt-6 mb-3">C. Information from Third-Party Integrations (Google APIs)</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">If you choose to integrate your Google Accounts (such as Google Business Profile and Google Search Console) with our platform, we will request your explicit authorization via OAuth.</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Data Retrieved:</strong> We access your Google Business Profile data (reviews, local posts, business information) and Google Search Console data (analytics, indexing status) to display within your dashboard and automate responses or reporting.</li>
          <li><strong>Google API Services User Data Policy:</strong> Restoration AI's use and transfer to any other app of information received from Google APIs will adhere to the <a href="https://developers.google.com/terms/api-services-user-data-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline">Google API Services User Data Policy</a>, including the Limited Use requirements.</li>
          <li><strong>Data Usage:</strong> Data retrieved from Google APIs is used solely to provide the features you connected your account for. It is not used for advertising, profiling, or shared with third parties for purposes unrelated to the service.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">We use the collected information for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8 space-y-2">
          <li>To provide, operate, and maintain our Services.</li>
          <li>To process payments and manage your wallet balance.</li>
          <li>To operate our AI Receptionist, including listening to, recording, and transcribing incoming and outgoing calls to triage leads and book appointments.</li>
          <li>To analyze AI call interactions for the purpose of improving agent accuracy, training the models, and ensuring quality assurance.</li>
          <li>To sync your marketing data and automate responses to reviews via Google Integrations.</li>
          <li>To communicate with you regarding updates, security alerts, and support messages.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">3. Call Recording and AI Transcriptions</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">Our core service involves routing phone calls to AI voice agents. All calls handled by the Restoration AI platform are recorded and transcribed.</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8 space-y-2">
          <li>By using our Services, you consent to the recording of these calls.</li>
          <li>You are strictly responsible for notifying your callers that they are being recorded and are interacting with an AI, in accordance with applicable federal and state laws.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">4. How We Share Your Information</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">We do not sell your personal data. We may share your information only in the following situations:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> With vendors, consultants, and hosting partners (e.g., Supabase, Retell AI, Twilio, Stripe) who need access to such information to carry out work on our behalf.</li>
          <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> If required to do so by law or in response to valid requests by public authorities (e.g., a court or a government agency).</li>
          <li><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> In connection with, or during negotiations of, any merger, sale of company assets, financing, or acquisition.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">5. Data Security and Retention</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">We implement commercially reasonable security measures designed to protect your information. Your OAuth tokens, user credentials, and database records are securely stored and encrypted.</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>General Retention:</strong> We retain your data, including call recordings and transcriptions, for as long as your account is active or as needed to provide you the Services, and to comply with our legal obligations.</li>
          <li><strong>Google API Data Retention:</strong> Google API data (Search Console analytics, Business Profile information) is retained as long as your account is active and deleted within 30 days of account closure or integration revocation.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">6. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">Depending on your location, you may have the right to request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data. You can manage your account information directly within the dashboard.</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Revoking Google Access:</strong> You may revoke our access to your Google account at any time from your account settings or directly via myaccount.google.com. Upon revocation, we will delete your stored Google OAuth tokens within 30 days.</li>
          <li><strong>Account Deletion:</strong> To request deletion of your call recordings or account data, please contact us. Note that certain financial records or wallet balance histories must be retained for accounting and compliance purposes.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at:</p>
        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:support@restorationai.io" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors">support@restorationai.io</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
